{"tid":1876952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港係中国既一部分，要求撒僑係反華丶支持港獨主張","createTime":"2020-02-12T17:38:51.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-14T16:15:03.000Z","uid":51200,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2fd7a1de53135b2131f6f8269aaedd4680daff68","tid":1876952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:38:51.000Z","msg":"你幾可見過住係同一個國家嘅人會撤僑<br />\n上海政府唔會係武漢撤僑<br />\n只有反華既外國政府先會，例如：美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n所以留喺湖北嘅港人<br />\n要求香港政府派專機撤離係分離主義，天理不容<br />\n貪得無厭<br />\n為國家同政府添亂<br />\n<br />\n係瘟疫橫行嘅年代<br />\n仲敢上去国內探親同拜年既<br />\n就應該乖乖地係上面安享晚年<br />\n國家好樂意為佢哋提供一條龍火化服務<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n盡顯大國之道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n利申：愛国藍絲<br />\n<br />\n認同請比讚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a34e0124c8134c3b550aceaaa2ae109c26d83b5","tid":1876952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:41:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c72579de1b6b73d6692abacabedde315f0a18fb7","tid":1876952,"uid":20442,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:44:22.000Z","msg":"憑咩香港人勞師動眾開機場撒僑？<br />\n<br />\n不顧及各省各地人民感受，又想引發內地人排港？<br />\n<br />\n為顧及大局，要相信中國政府大國能力，在湖北的香港人要忍讓、配合國家，不添煩添亂。<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ea0df446e80fac757507c30482709a93b0aadba","tid":1876952,"uid":279812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:45:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be4762933c8ba73632ebbdd6236b823a8d2c4874","tid":1876952,"uid":64743,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:45:07.000Z","msg":"我係呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026a3d8c97554e1936f6769208940b00ed6d96c5","tid":1876952,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"講得非常好"},{"pid":"c1703190fd5af482bee60082f03546fb2e80cc03","tid":1876952,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:49:20.000Z","msg":"香港係中国神聖不可分割既領土<br />\n唔存在派包機撤喬既權力<br />\n要相信火神山既醫療水平<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf160bd4f1b9a9d8ab035f43c465fe9cb9af94d2","tid":1876952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"026a3d8c97554e1936f6769208940b00ed6d96c5","tid":1876952,"uid":261796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-12T17:46:48.000Z","msg":"講得非常好"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T02:36:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73f7df854b935b9cf8a77f106623249338a0a3da","tid":1876952,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:15:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"987d057b05ab5e01cc3ee296e4f9fc99f56e8a4a","tid":1876952,"uid":278219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-13T12:23:05.000Z","msg":"認同請分享"},{"pid":"44cd015ac0276b59e3b9c5ee9a7d1a2de7b16f43","tid":18769